<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Requirements: Taming spot, Recipe, Stamina points (check fapet's recipe), any recipe related item/skill\n\nInfo: Taming is a special procedure (exploiting fapet's fetishes) to turn a wild fapet into your own slave\n\nNote:\n- If a taming procedure doesn't seem to work it's a good idea to review it's recipe, checking for any details\n- If you don't have enough stamina points the taming procedure will result in a failure, in some cases in a bad end\n- Some fapets might require more stamina (and overall be more challanging) for a succesfull taming\n\nTaming Expertise: stamina partially restores after taming (ex: Tamed 5'th bunny with 3 stam, restored 1 after taming).The amount of restored stamina can't be higher then the spent on taming. To tame you'd still need the required amount of stamina\n- 5 Tames %3D +1 stamina restored\n- 10 Tames %3D +2 stamina restored\n- 20 Tames %3D +3 stamina restored\n- 40 Tames %3D +4 stamina restored \n\nNotes:\n- (for selling) Some fapets by default are pricier then others (usually if their taming procedure is more complex then the selling price would also be higher)=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Zahteve: mesto za ukroćenje, recept, točke vzdržljivosti (preverite recept za fapeta), kateri koli predmet/spretnja, povezana z receptom\n\nInformacije: ukroćenje je poseben postopek (izkoriščanje fapetovih fetišev) za spreminjanje divjadi fapet v lastnega sužnja\n\nOpomba:\n- Če se zdi, da postopek ukrotenja ne deluje, je dobro, da pregledate njegov recept in preverite morebitne podrobnosti\n- Če nimate dovolj vzdržljivosti točk ukrotenja postopek bo povzročil neuspeh, v nekaterih primerih pa tudi slab konec\n- Nekateri fapeti bodo morda potrebovali več vzdržljivosti (in na splošno bolj zahtevni) za uspešno ukrotitev\n\nStrokovnost ukrotenja: vzdržljivost se delno povrne po ukrotitvi (npr. Tamed 5 '-ti zajček s 3 stam, obnovljen 1 po ukrotitvi). Količina obnovljene vzdržljivosti ne more biti višja od porabljene za ukrotitev. Za ukrotitev bi še vedno potrebovali potrebno količino vzdržljivosti\n- 5 Tames %3D +1 vzdržljivost obnovljena\n- 10 Tames %3D +2 vzdržljivost obnovljena\n- 20 Tames %3D +3 vzdržljivost obnovljena\n- 40 Tames %3D +4 vzdržljivost obnovljena \n\nOpombe:\n- (za prodajo) Nekateri fapeti so privzeto dražji od drugih (običajno, če je njihov postopek ukrotitve bolj zapleten, bi bila tudi prodajna cena višja)
<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Forced rapes with worser consequences\n\nAchieve: failed taming, force rapes (with 0 stamina/energy)=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Prisilna posilstva s hujšimi posledicami\n\nDoseči: neuspešno ukrotitev, prisilna posilstva (z 0 vzdržljivosti/energije)
<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Special actions which can be perfomed during an hAct. Primarily their funtion is to boost the partner's arrousment\nBasics:\n- h-actions are replacing quickslots, being shown at the bottom of the screen, they can be activated by holding pressed the according number key (on keyboard above letters QWERT) 1,2, etc. The one in left corner is Cancel/Stop [0 key], it'll cancel th hAct upon getting the appearing gauge filled. It's filling speed depends on character's arrousment, higher arr - slower filling speed.\nNot all hActs have h-actions. Forced and attacking hActs have no canceling\n\nNotes:\n- If one of them is displayed as locked, then it can probably be unlocked by having multiple hacts or increasing their h-experience=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Posebna dejanja, ki se lahko izvajajo med hAct. Njihova naloga je predvsem povečati partnerjevo vznemirjenost\nOsnove:\n- h-dejanja nadomeščajo hitre reže, prikazane so na dnu zaslona, aktivirate jih lahko z držanjem ustrezne številske tipke (na tipkovnici nad črkami QWERT) 1 ,2 itd. Tisti v levem kotu je Prekliči/Ustavi [0 tipka], bo preklical hAct, ko bo prikazani merilnik napolnjen. Njegova hitrost polnjenja je odvisna od vznemirjenosti lika, višji arr - počasnejša hitrost polnjenja.\nVsa dejanja nimajo h-akcij. Prisilni in napadajoči hActs nimajo preklica\n\nOpombe:\n- Če je eden od njih prikazan kot zaklenjen, ga je verjetno mogoče odkleniti z več napadi ali povečati njihovo h-izkušnjo
<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Energy is used for exhausting activities such as running, comforting in hActs or attempting an escape from an hAct. Some states affect the drain and replenish rate (ex: pregnant mode).\n\nNotes:\n- In some cases energy's cap can lower. It can only be restored by sleeping in comfort (in a house/room)=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Energija se uporablja za izčrpavajoče dejavnosti, kot so tek, tolažba v hAktih ali poskus pobega iz hAkta. Nekatera stanja vplivajo na hitrost praznjenja in polnjenja (npr. način nosečnosti).\n\nOpombe:\n- V nekaterih primerih se lahko zgornja meja energije zniža. Obnoviti ga je mogoče le z udobnim spanjem (v hiši/sobi)
<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>- Day can be passed if sleeping in house (via interacting with the bed)\n- The character will also restore some stats (stamina, energyCap) while sleeping\n- Higher lvl houses give higher stats restoration=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>- Dan lahko pretečete, če spite v hiši (prek interakcije s posteljo)\n- Lik bo med spanjem obnovil tudi nekatere statistične podatke (vzdržljivost, EnergyCap)\n- Hiše višjega nivoja dajejo obnovitev višje statistike
<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Hold F2 to toggle between fast arrousment filling and normal speed\n\nApplies globally (on everything and everyone)\n\nNote: can cause some bugs (mostly limited to visual type)=<align%3Dleft><size%3D25>Pridržite F2 za preklapljanje med hitrim polnjenjem vznemirjenja in normalno hitrostjo\n\nVelja globalno (na vse in vsakogar)\n\nOpomba: lahko povzroči nekaj napak (večinoma omejeno na vizualni tip)

Ok, here's a quick course on CrowdQuests=Ok, tukaj je hiter tečaj o CrowdQuests
1. Crowd Chars with an indicator above their heads are interactable NPCs=1. Množični znaki z indikatorjem nad glavami so NPC-ji, ki lahko komunicirajo
2. Indicator colors: Blueish - AvailableQuest, Gray - InProgress Quest, Green - Finished Quest, Orange - Shop=2. Barve indikatorjev: modrikasta - na voljoQuest, siva - iskanje v teku, zelena - končana naloga, oranžna - nakupovanje
3. Book: registers active quests (icon showing if it's in progress or finished), and on Select - Highlights the NPC in the world (look around for a blueish beam)=3. Knjiga: registrira aktivne naloge (ikona, ki prikazuje, ali je v teku ali je končana), in na Select - Poudari NPC na svetu (poglej okoli za modrikasti žarek)
4. Tips: Interacting with the NPC will show the current progress and will Highlight the target's location (in some cases)=4. Nasveti: Interakcija z NPC bo pokazala trenutni napredek in označila lokacijo tarče (v nekaterih primerih)

3. Get the Piss Gauge to 100% by natural waiting (if already 99%), or by eating a diuretic pill (pill's slot select [1 or 2] > Use [RMB])=3. 4. After tamer is done pissing, stand up and get a little away from it - Warg will approach to sniff tamer's territory marking (thinking that this is a challenge for territory). Keep your distance and stay on guard, once he's done sniffing he'll start running after you=4. Ko je krotilec končal picati, vstanite in se malo odmaknite od njega - Warg bo pristopil, da bo povohal označevanje ozemlja ukrotitelja (v mislih, da je to izziv za ozemlje). Držite razdaljo in ostanite na straži, ko bo končal z vohanjem, bo začel teči za vami
5. Run to the nearby taming spot=5. Tecite do bližnjega mesta za ukrotitev
6. Stop and let him approach you=6. Ustavite se in mu dovolite, da se vam približa

4. Go behind him and crouch - sniff his back > he'll notice that and will safely follow you for a little while (~35 sec).
